Nevada: Exchange QHPs up to 47.2K (74% paid)
Wed, 05/14/2014 - 3:08pm
Minor update out of the only state whose ACA exchange is stillofficiallyopen: QHPs up around 1,400, paid up around 200 since last week:
Update as of 5/10: 47,245 Nevadans confirm Qualified Health Plan selections. 35,034 have paid.
